metadata.name: The national flag of Pepeland
metadata.description:
This is the national flag of Pepeland.
The green color symbolizes the foundation of this state - the majestic nature and the inhabitants of this state.
The white color symbolizes purity, freedom of vision and simplicity, which are the power of Ethereum.
The red color symbolizes the beauty of the smiles of the inhabitants of this state.
The blue color symbolizes the national dress of the inhabitants of Pepeland.
